data.description: Your home search ends here! Welcome to this beautifully renovated 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home. This home was completely redone in 2021 from flooring to siding and has been meticulously maintained since.  The kitchen features stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Three cozy bedrooms and a beautiful modern style bathroom. Lastly, enjoy the huge back yard for family time and entertaining. Quick drive to the interstate for easy access to bases and all that Hampton Roads has to offer.
